{"tid":506825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警偷29蚊耳筒斷正　涉盜竊被捕","createTime":"2017-12-22T14:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T15:31:29.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e820297718a0f4723f5d3b8eabae3aabe882d316","tid":506825,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"今(22日)晚上7時許，深水埗福華街161至175號一間店舖內，一名54歲姓張休班警員在店內購買一些手機配件，他離開時被姓黃39歲男職員發現他身上一對耳筒未有付款，價值為29元。職員懷疑有人順手牽羊，於是報警求助。警方接報到場，以涉嫌盜竊拘捕該名休班警員。他已獲准保釋候查，須於本月下旬向警方報到。案件交由深水埗警區刑事部人員跟進。警方表示，如任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊會嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/143715?utm_content=buffer12df2&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F143715%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer12df2%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=4MxJQVgQqs6CX8oCnslF2DANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=60fa2638\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/143715?utm_content=buffer12df2&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>29蚊都去偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ef24463764989d5e8c4c69e3241992764c7697","tid":506825,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"召喚邱頒景"},{"pid":"5f3ec6e1253b737271604c3e9888fe5493810e8c","tid":506825,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"警超聯巴打去左邊"},{"pid":"071befecae4a0771186b1042d679dcbb6605cfca","tid":506825,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"165245c0195d5312a83dae1817d9340974d337da","tid":506825,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" c